---
import BaseLayout from '../layouts/BaseLayout.astro';
---
<BaseLayout title="About" description="About Project Notes.">
  <section class="page-header">
    <p class="eyebrow">About</p>
    <h1>About</h1>
    <p>This page is reserved for personal positioning, technical interests, project history, and contact details.</p>
  </section>
  <section class="two-column">
    <div>
      <h2>Site Direction</h2>
      <p>This is a personal project lab and technical review archive, focused on real projects, engineering tradeoffs, and reusable lessons.</p>
    </div>
    <div>
      <h2>Next Steps</h2>
      <p>Future versions can add richer indexes, search, tags, automation, and long-term knowledge workflows.</p>
    </div>
  </section>
</BaseLayout>
